oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Joe Lee Discs from June 14, 1940 to August 19, 1940
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recordings are compromised from a variety of recordings of: Joe Lee (entertainer), Paul Ray (entertainer), Jimmie Smith (entertainer), and the Wyoming Rangers (performance group). The recordings are from June 14, 1940, June 19, 1940, August 04, 1940, and August 19, 1940.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Joe Lee; Jimmie Smith; Wyoming Rangers; Paul Ray
